{"tid":1927945,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"中華人民共和國《網絡安全法》的魔鬼細節","createTime":"2020-03-16T05:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-16T05:53:11.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c5140511b731270321c4d925e231b12abbdceb55","tid":1927945,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T05:53:11.000Z","msg":"點解大陸block google<br />\n有咩法律依據<br />\n一齊探討研究下<br />\n<br />\n中華人民共和國《網絡安全法》<br />\n全文在這裏<br />\n<br />\nWiki <br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%B3%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikisource.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%258D%258E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%2585%25B1%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%259B%25BD%25E7%25BD%2591%25E7%25BB%259C%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%25B3%2595&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvtXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=b29c1290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/%E4%B8%AD%E5%8D%8E%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%B1%E5%92%8C%E5%9B%BD%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E6%B3%95</a><br />\n<br />\nOfficial<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.csrc.gov.cn/pub/newsite/flb/flfg/flxzsf/201805/t20180518_338285.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.csrc.gov.cn%2Fpub%2Fnewsite%2Fflb%2Fflfg%2Fflxzsf%2F201805%2Ft20180518_338285.html&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2BvtXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=77a610ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.csrc.gov.cn/pub/newsite/flb/flfg/flxzsf/201805/t20180518_338285.html</a><br />\n<br />\n魔鬼細節在這裏<br />\n<br />\n第四十七条 网络运营者<strong>应当加强对其用户发布的信息的管理，</strong>发现<strong>法律、行政法规禁止发布</strong>或者传输的信息的，<strong>应当立即停止传输该信息，</strong>采取消除等处置措施，<strong>防止信息扩散，保存有关记录，并向有关主管部门报告</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n第五十条 国家网信部门和有关部门依法履行网络信息安全监督管理职责，发现法律、行政法规禁止发布或者传输的信息的，应当要求网络运营者停止传输，采取消除等处置措施，保存有关记录；<strong>对来源于中华人民共和国境外的上述信息，应当通知有关机构采取技术措施和其他必要措施阻断传播。</strong>"}]}